transcripts.text: Mitch McConnell.  He's just as bad as Trump, and no one ever talks about it.  I suck.
Here's why.  The good guys won back the House in 2018, but thanks to this old weirdo, everything cool we tried to pass has died in the Senate.
Everything you hate about Washington is because this Mitch designed it that way.

Our top political priority over the next two years should be to deny President Obama a second term.  Obama would not fill this seat.  We will now try a different way to bring the American people relief from Obamacare.
But we can get rid of this little Mitch.  All we have to do is win a handful of Senate seats in a handful of states, and Mitch loses the majority and all of his creepy, terrifying power.
No, please, don't tell him my weakness is...
So when you're voting against Susan Collins in Maine, you're actually voting against this guy.

Or when you're voting against Cory Gardner in Colorado, you're actually voting against old resting Mitch face.  And in Alabama, Alaska, Arizona, Georgia, Iowa, North Carolina, South Carolina, and Texas, you may not see him...
But Mitch McConnell is on the ballot.

And if you happen to live in Kentucky, you can vote him out of office directly.  Whether you live in these states or not, 2020 is our one shot to finally wrestle the power away from Mitch's clammy, weird hands.
And we're launching a fund to do just that.  Get Mitch or die trying.
If you don't donate, I'm just going to be here forever.  Mitch McConnell.  You know what I do for fun?  Nothing.
